CMP #$77
BEQ PressUp
LDA $FF
CMP #$65
BEQ colorz
LDA $FF
CMP #$71
BEQ erase


JMP main

PressRight:


TXA
LDA $100
CLC
ADC #$01
STA $100
TAX

JSR resetbutton
JMP main

PressLeft:


TXA
LDA $100
SEC
SBC #$01
STA $100
TAX

JSR resetbutton
JMP main

PressDown:


TXA
LDA $100
CLC
ADC #$20
STA $100
TAX

JSR resetbutton
JMP main

PressUp:

TXA
LDA $100
SEC
SBC #$20
STA $100
TAX

JSR resetbutton
JMP main

colorz:
INC $12
JMP main

erase:
